Description:
On the ground, you find an ornate wooden crest, exquisitely crafted and radiating a powerful magical aura. An inscription is engraved on the crest, but some words are missing. The readable portion says:

“May the bearer receive the blessing of House…”

The crest is worn and weathered, making it impossible to discern the name of the house. However, you are certain that uncovering this information could unlock its magic.
DescriptionAction: What will you do with the crest?
